      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://gitee.com/wanli-0ziyuan/gitee-graph-bed/raw/master/img/20201023211243.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://gitee.com/wanli-0ziyuan/gitee-graph-bed/raw/master/img/20201023211243.jpg"></p><a id="more"></a><p>Welcome to <a href="https://0-ziyuan.com/">0ziyuan’s blog</a>! This is my very first post. Click <a href="https://0-ziyuan.com/about/">about</a> for more info. If you get any problems when visiting my blog, you can contact me through <a href="mailto:wanli@0-ziyuan.com">my email</a>. I’d be delighted if you fork me on <a href="https://github.com/0ziyuan?tab=repositories">GitHub</a>​.😄</p><h3 id="Why-I-build-this-blog-site"><a href="#Why-I-build-this-blog-site" class="headerlink" title="Why I build this blog site"></a>Why I build this blog site</h3><ol><li>记录学习；</li><li>分享交流；</li><li>Just for fun..😂</li></ol><h3 id="How-I-build-this-blog-site"><a href="#How-I-build-this-blog-site" class="headerlink" title="How I build this blog site"></a>How I build this blog site</h3><p>鉴于还是一个技术力和财力皆无的学生党，我是参照教程用Hexo生成静态页面，然后将代码托管到GitHub Pages上的方式创建网站的。博客主题为 Next下的Muse,文章编辑工具用的是Typora。主要参照教程如下，感兴趣的小伙伴可以康康：</p><ul><li><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/102592286?utm_source=qq&utm_medium=social&utm_oi=1124773277125697536">从零开始搭建个人博客（超详细）</a></p></li><li><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/69217131">网站ICP备案和公安备案流程</a></p></li><li><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/695283187b62">【官方支持】让个人域名下Github Pages完美支持https</a></p><p>注：教程有些bug，也可能与实际操作存在出入，不过应该都能百度解决，毕竟我就是这么干的😅(外加查看相关代码的文档)</p></li></ul><h3 id="In-the-end"><a href="#In-the-end" class="headerlink" title="In the end"></a>In the end</h3><p><em>Don’t try to understand it, feel it.</em></p>]]></content:encoded>
      
      
      
      
